WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.755
Android yaratuvchisi sifatida,

00:00:01.755 --> 00:00:04.815
mavjud bo‘lgan ilova kodiga qarab chiqish tanqidiy 
fikrni rivojlantiradi deb hisoblayman.

00:00:04.815 --> 00:00:06.449
Agar siz kelajakda bironta jamoaga qo‘shilsangiz, 

00:00:06.449 --> 00:00:08.370
siz eskizdan birontasini yaratishning o‘rniga, 

00:00:08.370 --> 00:00:09.810
mavjud bo‘lgan ilova ustida ishlashingiz mumkin.

00:00:09.810 --> 00:00:11.460
Ba’zi bir loyihalarda yuzlab fayllar bo‘lishi mumkin

00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:14.205
va siz ularni hammasini o‘qib chiqishingiz 
uchun vaqt bo‘lmasligi mumkin.

00:00:14.205 --> 00:00:18.000
Biroq, siz shunda ham fayl nomlariga qarab, keyin siz qilishingiz 
kerak bo‘lgan ishga taalluqli bo‘lgan fayllarga yana ham 

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.390
yaqinroqdan qarab chiqib yuqori darajali 
fikrga ega bo‘lishingiz mumkin.

00:00:21.390 --> 00:00:22.740
Demak, bu holatda, 

00:00:22.740 --> 00:00:24.060
bizda hozirda bitta kichkina loyiha bor, 

00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:27.720
biz nazorat savollarida sizdan har bitta faylga qarab 
chiqishingizni so‘ragandik, keling hozir uni birgalikda qilamiz.

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.960
Shunday qilib, men mana bu yerdagi project ga borish, 
uni loyiha view siga o‘zgartirish bilan boshlamoqchiman, 

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:35.175
va men birinchi marta asosiy kodga qaraganimda, 

00:00:35.175 --> 00:00:38.730
men ilovaning barcha mantig‘ini ichiga 
olgan Java faylni kengaytiraman.

00:00:38.730 --> 00:00:41.640
Keyin men u yerga boraman va 
ilovaning ko‘rinishiga tegishli 

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:44.070
barcha narsani ichiga olgan 
resource faylni kengaytiraman.

00:00:44.070 --> 00:00:46.950
Java faylda, bizda main activity 
deb nomlanadigan bitta java fayl bor 

00:00:46.950 --> 00:00:50.865
va u ko‘rsatadiki, main activity bizning 
ilovamizning asosiy oynasi.

00:00:50.865 --> 00:00:53.340
Endi biz ilovaning app/source/main/res 
yo‘lida joylashgan 

00:00:53.340 --> 00:00:58.365
resource fayllariga o‘tsak bo‘ladi.

00:00:58.365 --> 00:01:01.260
Bu fayllar ilova turli qurilmalarda 
qanday paydo bo‘lishini nazorat qiladi.

00:01:01.260 --> 00:01:04.320
Resource lar XML fayllarni, rasmlarni 
va boshqa ommaviy axborot vostalari 

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.450
fayllarini o‘z ichiga oladi.

00:01:06.450 --> 00:01:08.865
Biz layout faylini 
kengaytirishdan boshlasak bo‘lardi.

00:01:08.865 --> 00:01:12.855
Bu yerda bizda activity_main.xml fayli bor.

00:01:12.855 --> 00:01:15.840
Bu fayl ilovamizning asosiy oynasi 
uchun layoutni ifodalaydi va

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:18.810
u to‘rtta matn view li bitta vertikal 
chiziqli layoutdan tashkil topgan.

00:01:18.810 --> 00:01:20.445
Keyin bizda bitta faqatgina ilova ikonkasi uchun 

00:01:20.445 --> 00:01:23.100
maxsus bo‘lgan mipmap fayli bor.

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:26.400
Ilovangizdagi boshqa rasmlar 
Java faylga borishi kerak.

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:28.365
Keyin bizda qiymatlar fayli bor.

00:01:28.365 --> 00:01:30.780
Bu ilovamizning ranglarini, 
ilovaning mavzusi ranglarini va 

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:32.875
so‘zlarning har bir kategoriyasi bilan bog‘langan 

00:01:32.875 --> 00:01:36.585
ranglarni ifodalaydigan colors.xml fayldan tashkil topgan.

00:01:36.585 --> 00:01:38.760
Keyin bizda ilovamiz uchun misol uchun, 
kenglik va balandlik kabi yo‘nalishlardan 

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:42.195
tashkil topgan dimensions.xml fayli bor.

00:01:42.195 --> 00:01:44.310
U ham mana bu yerda 88 dpga tenglab qo‘yilgan ro‘yxat 

00:01:44.310 --> 00:01:47.175
elementining balandligidan tashkil topgan.

00:01:47.175 --> 00:01:49.905
Pastga tushsak, bizda strings.xml fayli bor.

00:01:49.905 --> 00:01:53.610
Bular hammasi ilovadagi foydalanuvchi 
uchun paydo bo‘ladigan matn string lari

00:01:53.610 --> 00:01:55.260
va biz ularni yagona faylga qo‘yamiz, shunda

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:57.495
biz ilovani boshqa tilga osongina tarjima qila olamiz.

00:01:57.495 --> 00:02:00.060
Va eng oxirgisi, bizda styles.xml fayli bor.

00:02:00.060 --> 00:02:03.205
Bu yerda biz ilovaning mavzusini ifodalaymiz va 
mavzuning rangini aniqlashtirib olamiz.

00:02:03.205 --> 00:02:06.630
Bizda kategoriya qanday ko‘rinishi uchun 
uslub ham bor va shuning uchun

00:02:06.630 --> 00:02:09.990
ilovaning asosiy ekranidagi har bir kategoriya 
balandlik, padding , shrift o‘lchami va boshqalar 

00:02:09.990 --> 00:02:12.330
bo‘yicha o‘xshash ko‘rinadi.

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:15.150
Demak, endi keling, topshiriqning 
ilovaning turli xil qismlari uchun 
 
