java faylning bo‘lishi 

00:02:33.370 --> 00:02:36.895
balki siz uchun muhim bo‘lgan qismi bo‘lgandir.

00:02:36.895 --> 00:02:40.005
Demak, bu yerda siz chiza olishingiz mumkin 
